PN,44901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FIn July 2025, an MP's office was
OL,7,Fcontacted by a member of the public
OL,8,Fwho said they were worried about what
OL,9,Fthey said were a number of cases of
OL,10,Fchildhood - young people's - cancer in
OL,11,Fthe mid-Ulster region.
OL,13,FThe MP's team was concerned by what
OL,14,Fthey read and contacted UTV to flag
OL,15,Fthe story but also as they trusted
OL,16,Fthat we would report this issue of
OL,17,Fhigh public interest responsibly.
OL,19,FThe member of the public was Hugh
OL,20,FMcCloy from Draperstown.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FHis daughter Freda, age only six, was
OL,7,Fin the middle of treatment for
OL,8,Fleukaemia. According to Hugh, when he
OL,9,Fspoke to other parents whose children
OL,10,Fwere also being treated for the same
OL,11,Fdeadly condition, he was struck by the
OL,12,Fnumber of cases from mid-Ulster. A
OL,13,Fthought which he says was shared by
OL,14,Fother parents.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FWhen there is a spike in a particular
OL,7,Ftype of cancer, in a certain age group
OL,8,For demographic who all live in a
OL,9,Fcertain area, this could constitute a
OL,10,Fcancer 'cluster.' The Northern Ireland
OL,11,FCancer Registry which is overseen by
OL,12,Fthe Public Health Authority monitors
OL,13,Fcancer rates and trends. At the same
OL,14,Ftime that he reached out to MPs, Hugh
OL,15,Falso contacted the Cancer Registry,
OL,16,Fthe Chief Medical Officer and the PHA.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FFOIs of communications between these
OL,7,Fdepartments show that the Chief
OL,8,FMedical Officer, Michael McBride asked
OL,9,Ffor childhood cancer rates to be
OL,10,Finvestigated. But almost one year
OL,11,Flater, Hugh and other families which
OL,12,FUTV has spoken to say they are
OL,13,Ffrustrated at a lack of answers and
OL,14,Furgency over what they say is a life
OL,15,Fand death matter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FThe key issue in question is the
OL,7,Ftimeframe. When Hugh contacted the
OL,8,Frelevant agencies, he was specific
OL,9,Fabout the period he was asking them to
OL,10,Flook at. Mid-July 2023 onwards. UTV
OL,11,Fhas been contacted by 10 families and
OL,12,Fyoung people whose children or who
OL,13,Fthemselves have developed cancer,
OL,14,Fgenerally leukaemia and Ewing's
OL,15,FSarcoma. Eight of those were diagnosed
OL,16,Fafter mid-July 2023.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FHugh met with the PHA in September
OL,7,F2025. He was left dissatisfied as he
OL,8,Fwas told verified data was only
OL,9,Favailable until the end of 2022. It
OL,10,Fdidn't cover the time frame he was
OL,11,Fasking about.
OL,13,FWhat Hugh didn't know is that by this
OL,14,Fpoint, the PHA had been contacted by a
OL,15,Fcampaign group 'Save the Moat' who
OL,16,Falso raised a concern about a cancer
OL,17,Fcluster in a similar area.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FThe FOIs which have been seen by UTV
OL,7,Fshow that the second concern was noted
OL,8,Fand a DOH official asked the PHA to
OL,9,Ftreat the two concerns together as
OL,10,Fthey referred to the same area.
OL,12,FThat official wrote: "I'm aware that
OL,13,Fyou are also considering another
OL,14,Falleged cancer cluster correspondence
OL,15,Fand these issues may or may not be
OL,16,Frelated. They do however relate to the
OL,17,Fsame geographical location.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,F"I have discussed this correspondence
OL,7,Fwith (chief medical officer) Michael
OL,8,FMcBride and we think it would be
OL,9,Fhelpful if this issue could be
OL,10,Fconsidered alongside the existing
OL,11,Fmatter already referred and in the
OL,12,Fwork you are taking forward with the
OL,13,FNI cancer registry."
OL,15,FIn January 2025, UTV attended a
OL,16,Fbackground briefing with the Public
OL,17,FHealth Agency. It was comprehensive
OL,18,Fbut again we were told that although
OL,19,Fthere was provisional data for 2023,
OL,20,Fverified data only went to the end of
OL,21,F2022.
OL,26,@oD@FpmoD@\pn
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FFor Hugh, he doesn't understand why
OL,7,Fthe process to verify data takes so
OL,8,Flong. All the children are treated in
OL,9,Fone hospital so how is it that the
OL,10,Fnumbers take so long to crunch? But
OL,11,Fthe PHA argues that it's not as simple
OL,12,Fas that and a process has to be
OL,13,Ffollowed.
OL,15,FHowever, UTV has seen more FOIs from
OL,16,FFebruary of this year where the PHA,
OL,17,FDepartment of Health, the Cancer
OL,18,FRegistry and the chief medical
OL,19,Fofficer's office are formulating a
OL,20,Fmedia statement in case Hugh's claims
OL,21,Fget to the media.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FThe line which was sent to the
OL,7,FDepartment of Health for approval was
OL,8,Fbrief.
OL,10,F"I am aware that the Northern Ireland
OL,11,FCancer Registry continuously
OL,12,Fscrutinises cancer data and I have not
OL,13,Fbeen made aware of any environmental
OL,14,Flinks to childhood cancer cases in the
OL,15,FMid Ulster area."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FThe FOIs show that the media statement
OL,7,Fwas vetoed by the special advisor to
OL,8,Fthe health minister on the grounds
OL,9,Fthat the data which had been analysed
OL,10,Fby the PHA did not cover the timeframe
OL,11,FHugh asked about.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,F"And now given the apparent
OL,7,Finflexibility of the data and no
OL,8,Fability of the Department or PHA to be
OL,9,Fable to do anything about it - what
OL,10,Fare steps are being taken by again
OL,11,Feither the PHA or Department to
OL,12,Fdetermine the validity or not of the
OL,13,Fclaims being made? Because simply
OL,14,Freferring to data from four years ago,
OL,15,Fbefore the timeframe being raised in
OL,16,Fthe allegation, isn't going to cut it.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,F"Given the claim from the families
OL,7,Fspecifically relates to the period of
OL,8,FJuly 23 to April 25, placing so much
OL,9,Femphasis on the review of the
OL,10,Fvalidated data up until 2022 is fairly
OL,11,Fmeaningless and will be stated as such
OL,12,Fby the local community.
OL,14,F"If the Minister is asked - which he
OL,15,Fwill be - if he can give an assurance
OL,16,Fthat the allegations of a cluster...
OL,17,Fhe will need a stronger line than only
OL,18,Fbeing able to say that the most recent
OL,19,Fvalidated data is only available up to
OL,20,F2022."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FHugh, the families and the campaigners
OL,7,Fare not the only ones pressing for
OL,8,Fanswers. In the past 24 hours, the
OL,9,Flocal MLA, Patsy McGlone received a
OL,10,Fresponse to his request to meet the
OL,11,FPHA and a meeting has been scheduled
OL,12,Ffor next week. The Mid-Ulster Council
OL,13,Fhas also confirmed to UTV that it has
OL,14,Fwritten to the PHA asking for an
OL,15,Finvestigation into the matter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FAnd almost a year on from looking for
OL,7,Fanswers, Hugh and a mum of another
OL,8,Fchild with leukaemia have been told
OL,9,Fthat their Freedom of Information
OL,10,Fqueries are vexatious. A move which
OL,11,FHugh calls 'a low blow.'
OL,13,FThe PHA insists that the due process
OL,14,Fneeds to be followed and that takes
OL,15,Ftime...but for the families of those
OL,16,Fchildren with potentially fatal
OL,17,Fconditions....time is something they
OL,18,Fcan't necessarily be sure they have.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FThe PHA has told UTV that it has
OL,7,F'"worked with the Northern Ireland
OL,8,FCancer Registry (NICR) to fully
OL,9,Fexplore the concerns raised by a
OL,10,Fmember of the public about childhood
OL,11,Fcancers, and has also met the
OL,12,Fchildhood cancer team at the Royal
OL,13,FBelfast Hospital for Sick Children.
OL,14,FDetailed analysis showed that
OL,15,Fchildhood cancers in and within the
OL,16,FMid Ulster area were entirely
OL,17,Fconsistent with the rates across
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FIt continued: "The PHA, working with
OL,7,FNICR, has committed to keeping the
OL,8,Fdata under review and as validated
OL,9,Fdata become available, further
OL,10,Fanalysis will be carried out. The PHA
OL,11,Fand NICR have offered to meet any
OL,12,Ffamily who has concerns regarding this
OL,13,Fissue, and that offer remains open.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,F"In-depth data analysis has been
OL,7,Fcompleted in line with standard
OL,8,Fpractice and showed that the
OL,9,Fincidences of childhood cancer in and
OL,10,Fwithin the Mid Ulster Parliamentary
OL,11,FConstituency (PC) were entirely
OL,12,Fconsistent with rates across Northern
OL,13,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G18/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44919
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,F"This covered the time period 2018-
OL,7,F2022 (confirmed cases) and considering
OL,8,Fprovisional cases for the period 2018-
OL,9,F2023 (provisional cases for 2023). The
OL,10,Fcluster analysis was carried out using
OL,11,Frecognised methods applied by cancer
OL,12,Fregistries across the UK. Validated
OL,13,Fdata for subsequent years are not yet
OL,14,Favailable. The time taken for the
OL,15,Fvalidation of data is in line with
OL,16,Fother cancer registries in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G19/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44920
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,F"In addition, the PHA shared the
OL,7,Fconcerns with the childhood cancer
OL,8,Fteam at the Royal Belfast Hospital for
OL,9,FSick Children who treat all children
OL,10,Fwith cancer in Northern Ireland to
OL,11,Fexplore whether they had any concerns
OL,12,Fin relation to childhood cancer rates
OL,13,Fin more recent years in Northern
OL,14,FIreland or in the Mid Ulster area in
OL,15,Fparticular. They did not.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G20/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44921
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1778486754
OL,3,CMystery surrounds Mid-Ulster 'cancer
OL,4,Ccluster'
OL,6,FIt is vital that analysis of case
OL,7,Fnumbers and cancer rates is done in a
OL,8,Fscientifically rigorous way, looking
OL,9,Fat patterns in suitable geographical
OL,10,Fareas and over appropriate time
OL,11,Fperiods, ensuring that cases are
OL,12,Fcomplete, properly categorised and
OL,13,Fthat the analysis is done in a
OL,14,Fconsistent way. Taking pieces of
OL,15,Finformation in isolation, without the
OL,16,Ffull detail or out of context, can
OL,17,Flead to erroneous conclusions being
OL,18,Fdrawn."
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G21/22
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
